title: GATES / ANOTHERBABE barks
description: One of Measurehead's awesomely hot companions who barks mocking stuff at you (on clicking).

dialogueTree.title: Measurehead's Babe: ""No one will get past you!""

dialogueTree.english: "I dream about you all the time."
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Мару пра цябе без ані імгненнага адпачынку».

dialogueTree.title: Measurehead's Babe: ""Just look at him, the wonderful hu..."
dialogueTree.english: "Just look at him, the wonderful hunk."

dialogueTree.title: Measurehead's Babe: ""Not soft and weak like other men.""

dialogueTree.belarusian: «Не тое, што іншыя мужчыны, слабакі і слабаевцы».

dialogueTree.title: Measurehead's Babe: ""Everyone should try to be more lik..."
